Instructions to run the application.


1. Make a temporary directory to run the application in as follows
mkdir test-api
cd test-api
virtualenv flask
flask/bin/pip install flask


2. Now run the application as follows

chmod a+x app.py
$ ./app.py
 * Running on http://127.0.0.1:5000/
 * Restarting with reloader


3. In the browser, use any of the endpoints that you want to test.
example:

http://localhost:5000/users
will get users


4. For running unit-tests:
pip install pytest

# and then run
pytest


5. Testing by specifying filename
in file app_lib.py, please change the user_file_name and user_group_name to specify a file
